obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line 2
  line `THE REPEALING AND AMENDING ACT, 2019`
  line `A CT NO. 31 OF 2019`
  line `[8 th August, 2019.]`
  line `An Act to repeal certain enactments and to amend certain other enactments.`
  line `B E it enacted by Parliament in the Seventieth Year of the Republic of India as follows:—`
  line `1. Short title. —This Act may be called the Repealing and Amending Act, 2019.`
  line `2. Repeal of certain enactments. —The enactments specified in the First Schedule are hereby`
  line repealed.
  line `3. Amendment of certain enactments. —The enactments specified in the Second Schedule are`
  line `hereby amended to the extent and in the manner specified in the fourth column thereof.`
  line `4. Savings. —The repeal by this Act of any enactment shall not affect any other enactment in`
  line `which the repealed enactment has been applied, incorporated or referred to;`
  line `and this Act shall not affect the validity, invalidity, effect or consequences of anything already`
  line `done or suffered, or any right, title, obligation or liability already acquired, accrued or incurred, or any`
  line `remedy or proceeding in respect thereof, or any release or discharge of or from any debt, penalty,`
  line `obligation, liability, claim or demand, or any indemnity already granted, or the proof of any past act`
  line `or thing;`
  line `nor shall this Act affect any principle or rule of law, or established jurisdiction, form or course of`
  line `pleading, practice or procedure, or existing usage, custom, privilege, restriction, exemption, office or`
  line `appointment, notwithstanding that the same respectively may have been in any manner affirmed or`
  line `recognised or derived by, in or from any enactment hereby repealed;`
  line `nor shall the repeal by this Act of any enactment revive or restore any jurisdiction, office, custom,`
  line `liability, right, title, privilege, restriction, exemption, usage, practice, procedure or other matter or`
  line `thing not now existing or in force.`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
